ting thousands of words about them has not been easy, and I think it shows.=
=C2=A0
There=E2=80=99s this sequence that=E2=80=99s almost become a routine in our=
 house. I=E2=80=99ll stay up late Monday night and wake up really early on =
Tuesday morning to finish an essay, often rewriting it entirely from 5am - =
8:50am when the narrative structure finally shows itself. I=E2=80=99ll hit =
send, tweet about the essay, and then refresh Twitter for a while to see if=
