h of which is written by new people with novel perspectives.
And if I=E2=80=99m being realistic, I think my writing this year has been f=
ine. I=E2=80=99ve written some pieces that I really like, and that I think =
will stand up well to the test of time, but I do feel like generally, I=E2=
=80=99ve lost a little heat on my fastball and haven=E2=80=99t thrown enoug=
h screwballs.=C2=A0
This isn=E2=80=99t just in my head. I talked to a really perceptive founder=
