irect/6c7bb482-c3cf-43bc-bf0a-514f0d366d30?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7Gn=
A_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ].=C2=A0
Figuratively, what=E2=80=99s kept me up at night is fundraising.=C2=A0
In the beginning of 2023, the very first post I wrote, I announced that I w=
as raising Not Boring Capital Fund III [ https://substack.com/redirect/3950=
f612-c3d4-44ab-877b-ad5260a6364d?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZj=
mlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], a $30 million fund.=C2=A0
