If you=E2=80=99ve been following the venture news, you=E2=80=99ve probably =
read that it=E2=80=99s a brutal market for venture fundraising, that it=E2=
=80=99s particularly brutal for emerging managers, and that it=E2=80=99s tr=
iply brutal for emerging managers who raised their first funds at the peak =
in 2021.=C2=A0
All of that is true, but it isn=E2=80=99t productive and it doesn=E2=80=99t=
