ifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64=
, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">DIMO</a><span> among others, and it=
&#8217;s starting to pay off. There will be more to come here.&#160;</span>=
</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;=
 margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>On the team side, working with </span><a href=
=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/2627f754-6a0c-4693-bfd2-a060c7db9830?j=3D=
eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=
=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Elliot</a><span> a=
nd learning about the mind blowing things happening in bio has been a highl=
ight. Elliot&#8217;s combination of science, code, writing, investing disci=
pline, and ability to dream about the future is incredibly rare, and I full=
y expect him to be one of the best techbio investors to ever do it when all=
 is said and done.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>I&#8217;m incred=
ibly bullish on our strategy as the most important companies shift from pur=
e software companies to those that </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/r=
edirect/146d8ea6-3e3f-4dda-9e70-6aa8ead77db4?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7=
GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); =
text-decoration: underline;">combine bits and atoms</a><span>, and as the w=
orld shifts from centralization to </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/r=
edirect/1e039f92-2d91-491e-b4dc-7503c899dccd?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7=
GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); =
text-decoration: underline;">decentralization</a><span>. We can live in an =
Age of Miracles, and we want to continue to back the founders who are going=
 to bring it about. The crazier the better.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"col=
or: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0=
;"><span>We&#8217;re still raising (I&#8217;ll probably be raising until I =
die). </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/0a03ec70-db7f-427f-8d=
c9-616f57d0b2ef?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8=
ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">=
Get in touch if you want to be a part of it</a><span>.&#160;</span></p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>Optimism. </strong><span>One of the things I&#8217;m =
proudest of is that we planted an </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/re=
direct/1d11b0e9-8d60-4328-9fd6-da3bc54e7cec?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7G=
nA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); t=
ext-decoration: underline;">optimistic</a><span> flag early and we&#8217;ve=
 stuck with it through thick and thin.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: r=
gb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">As=
 the markets tumbled and wars raged, it was very easy to get views and list=
ens by telling people how awful things were. Pessimism will always sound sm=
art and responsible. Showing LPs that you&#8217;re being cautious builds tr=
ust, even if it&#8217;s the wrong move at precisely the wrong time.&#160;</=
p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; m=
argin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>As I wrote in the first ever Not Boring, </span><=
a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/eda71837-78f7-4f19-a8a2-a6cd0101709=
6?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Not Boring New=
sletter #1</a><span> &#8211; delayed by a couple of days because I caught e=
arly COVID:&#160;</span></p><div class=3D"captioned-image-container-static"=
